          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Good job!\n\nToday you've learned that relations are extremely important for us humans (and dogs won't hold grudge, but humans may). You've practiced your pause skills, so when something happens you can try to be in the moment. And you've identified friendship skills that matter to you, and decided to take action on two of them."
